    <main id="main" class="site-main inner-main">
      <section id="banner" class="notice reveal" style="display:none;"><strong id="banner1">Travana Tacos is not currently in operation.</strong><span id="banner2">First event: Rochester Lilac Festival (May 8–17, 2026). Serving Fri–Sun all day.</span></section>

      <section class="card reveal">
        <div class="section-top"><div><div class="kicker"><span class="k-dot"></span>Contact + booking</div><h1 style="margin-top:14px;">Let’s talk tacos.</h1><p class="lead">If you want Travana at your event, have a question, or just want to reach the people behind the stand, this is the cleanest place to start.</p></div><aside class="mini-quote">Fast answer, real details, no corporate tone. Just the family behind the food.</aside></div>
        <div class="contact-lead-grid">
          <div class="contact-shell">
            <ul class="contactlist">
              <li><span class="label">Email</span><span><a id="emailLink" href="mailto:travis.woods@travanatacos.com">travis.woods@travanatacos.com</a><span class="faint">&nbsp;·&nbsp;</span><button class="btn ghost" type="button" data-copy="emailLink" style="padding:8px 10px;border-radius:12px;">Copy</button></span></li>
              <li><span class="label">Instagram</span><a id="igLink" href="https://instagram.com/TravanaTacos" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@TravanaTacos</a></li>
              <li><span class="label">Payments</span><span class="muted">Card only (no cash)</span></li>
            </ul>
            <div class="contact-trust"><div class="trust-card"><div class="iconbadge" aria-hidden="true">📅</div><h3>Best for bookings</h3><p>Email is the cleanest move when you have a date, guest count, or event logistics to share.</p></div><div class="trust-card"><div class="iconbadge" aria-hidden="true">📱</div><h3>Best for quick updates</h3><p>Instagram is better for fast questions, location follow-up, and festival-week energy.</p></div></div>
            <div class="dual-cta"><a class="btn" href="/find-us.html">Find us</a><span class="status-chip inline-chip">Card only</span><a class="btn secondary" href="/menu.html">View menu</a></div>
          </div>
          <div class="note-box"><div class="overline">What helps us answer fast</div><h2 style="margin-top:8px;">The more clearly we can picture the event, the faster we can help.</h2><div class="booking-grid" style="margin-top:18px;"><div class="booking-card"><strong>Date + time</strong><p>Include service window, setup window, and any hard arrival times.</p></div><div class="booking-card"><strong>Guest count</strong><p>Even a rough number helps us think about pace and service flow.</p></div><div class="booking-card"><strong>Power + space</strong><p>Booth dimensions, access notes, and power availability save time fast.</p></div><div class="booking-card"><strong>Location</strong><p>Venue or event address helps us understand the logistics right away.</p></div></div></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="grid2">
        <section class="card reveal"><div class="kicker"><span class="k-dot"></span>Quick inquiry template</div><h2 style="margin-top:12px;">Copy, customize, send</h2><p class="muted" style="margin-top:8px;">A fast starting point for private events, partnerships, and festival conversations.</p><pre class="emailtemplate" id="templateText" style="margin-top:16px;">Subject: Travana Tacos Inquiry — [Event Name / Date]

Hi Travana Tacos,

My name is [Name]. I’m reaching out about [event / partnership / catering] on [date/time] at [location].
Expected headcount: [#]
Details: [Anything important — power, space, timing, etc.]

Best way to reach me: [phone/email]

Thanks!
[Name]</pre><div class="dual-cta" style="margin-top:18px;"><button class="btn secondary" type="button" data-copy="templateText">Copy template</button><a class="btn secondary" href="mailto:travis.woods@travanatacos.com?subject=Travana%20Tacos%20Inquiry">Open email</a></div></section>

        <section class="card card-dark reveal"><div class="kicker"><span class="k-dot"></span>Fast message builder</div><h2 style="margin-top:12px;">Generate an email in one step</h2><p class="muted" style="margin-top:8px;">No backend form needed. This opens your email app with the details already filled in.</p>
          <form class="form" id="mailtoForm">
            <div class="field"><label for="name">Your name</label><input id="name" name="name" autocomplete="name" placeholder="Name" /></div>
            <div class="field"><label for="reason">What’s this about?</label><select id="reason" name="reason"><option value="">Select…</option><option>Event inquiry</option><option>Partnership</option><option>Catering</option><option>General question</option></select></div>
            <div class="field"><label for="date">Date / time (optional)</label><input id="date" name="date" placeholder="e.g., May 10, 2026 at 6pm" /></div>
            <div class="field"><label for="headcount">Expected headcount (optional)</label><input id="headcount" name="headcount" inputmode="numeric" placeholder="e.g., 150" /></div>
            <div class="field"><label for="phone">Best callback number (optional)</label><input id="phone" name="phone" autocomplete="tel" inputmode="tel" placeholder="e.g., (585) 555-1234" /></div>
            <div class="field"><label for="details">Details</label><textarea id="details" name="details" placeholder="Space, power needs, timing, location, anything important…"></textarea></div>
            <div class="dual-cta"><button class="btn" type="submit">Generate email</button><a class="btn secondary" id="emailLink2" href="mailto:travis.woods@travanatacos.com">Or just email us</a></div>
            <div class="buttons" style="margin-top:8px;"><a class="btn ghost" id="igLink2" href="https://instagram.com/TravanaTacos" target="_blank" rel="noopener">DM us on Instagram</a></div>
          </form>
        </section>
      </section>

      <section class="card card-sunset reveal"><div class="kicker"><span class="k-dot"></span>Response-ready details</div><h2 style="margin-top:12px;">What helps us answer faster</h2><div class="contact-trust" style="margin-top:18px;"><div class="trust-card"><div class="iconbadge" aria-hidden="true">📅</div><h3>Date + timing</h3><p>Include the event date, serving window, and any setup constraints right away.</p></div><div class="trust-card"><div class="iconbadge" aria-hidden="true">👥</div><h3>Guest count</h3><p>An estimate makes it easier to suggest the right setup and pace.</p></div><div class="trust-card"><div class="iconbadge" aria-hidden="true">⚡</div><h3>Power / space</h3><p>Even rough notes about booth space and power access can save time later.</p></div><div class="trust-card"><div class="iconbadge" aria-hidden="true">📍</div><h3>Location</h3><p>Tell us where the event is happening so logistics are easier to picture instantly.</p></div></div></section>

      <footer class="footer footer-rich"><div class="footer-inner"><div class="footer-center"><img src="/images/TravanaLogo.png" alt="Travana Tacos" class="footer-logo" /><div class="footer-title">© <span id="y"></span> <span id="brandName2">Travana Tacos</span></div><div class="mini">Rochester pride. Mexican flavor roots. One taco done right.</div><div class="footer-socials"><a href="https://instagram.com/TravanaTacos" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a><a href="mailto:travis.woods@travanatacos.com">Email</a><a href="/find-us.html">Find Us</a></div><div class="footer-news">For bookings, partnerships, and questions, this is the straightest line to us.</div></div></div></footer>
    </main>
